                    <li><strong>Contact Details</strong> (if necessary)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>All information is collected strictly for the purpose of processing the verification.</p>

                <h2>3. Sources of Verification</h2>
                <p>Verify My KYC verifies identities using:</p>
                <ul class="checklist">
                    <li><strong>Government-authorized APIs</strong> (e.g., UIDAI for Aadhaar verification)</li>
                    <li><strong>Official government databases and records</strong></li>
