                </ul>

                <h2>6. Compliance</h2>
                <p>Our verification processes comply with applicable:</p>
                <ul class="checklist">
                    <li><strong>KYC (Know Your Customer) regulations</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>AML (Anti-Money Laundering) laws</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>Data protection and privacy legislation</strong> in the jurisdictions we operate in</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We ensure verifications are conducted lawfully and responsibly.</p>

